headline: Brookfield and Bloom Energy Announce $5 Billion Strategic AI Infrastructure Partnership
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., October 13, 2025--Bloom Energy (NYSE: BE), a global leader in power solutions, and Brookfield today announced a $5 billion strategic partnership to implement a reimagined future for AI infrastructure. This partnership marks the first phase of a joint vision to build AI factories capable of meeting the growing compute and power demands of artificial intelligence.
